trans-unit.source: Specifies the types of framework-level property behavior that pertain to a particular dependency property in the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] property system.
trans-unit.target: Anger vilka typer av framework nivå egenskap som hör till en viss beroendeegenskap i den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] egenskapen system.

trans-unit.source: Use this enumeration when you construct a <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata> instance where you want to specify one or more the framework-level metadata option settings.
trans-unit.target: Använd den här uppräkningen när du skapar en <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata>instans där du vill ange en eller flera framework nivå metadata inställningarna.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata>

trans-unit.source: You no longer use this enumeration after the constructor call.
trans-unit.target: Du kan inte längre använda den här uppräkningen efter konstruktoranrop.

trans-unit.source: Instead, query the particular metadata option that was set during registration by checking the `true` or `false` value of a specific property of an existing <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata>.
trans-unit.target: I stället frågan viss metadata alternativ som angavs under registreringen genom att kontrollera den `true` eller `false` värdet för en specifik egenskap i en befintlig <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata>.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata>

trans-unit.source: These property names match the FrameworkPropertyMetadataOptions enumeration values except for NotDataBindable, which is <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata.IsNotDataBindable%2A> on the finished <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata>.
trans-unit.target: Dessa egenskapsnamn matchar FrameworkPropertyMetadataOptions uppräkningsvärdena förutom NotDataBindable, som är <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata.IsNotDataBindable%2A>färdiga <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata>.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata> </xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata.IsNotDataBindable%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Journal option only specifies the intention to be journaled.
trans-unit.target: Alternativet Journal anger bara att vara journalförda.

trans-unit.source: The actual journaling may or may not be addressed by journaling services such as those that are present in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] viewer application.
trans-unit.target: Den faktiska journalnivåer kan eller kan inte tas upp journalnivåer tjänster, till exempel de som finns i den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] visningsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: In particular, journaling has some known limitations if the element tree was constructed through code rather than [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: I synnerhet journalnivåer har vissa kända begränsningar om trädet element har konstruerats med kod i stället [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: For details, see [Navigation Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i [Navigeringsöversikt](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Although property value inheritance might appear to work for nonattached dependency properties, the inheritance behavior for a nonattached property through certain element boundaries in the runtime tree is undefined.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Även om värdet egenskapsarv kan visas för bilaga beroendeegenskaper arv beteendet för en bilaga egenskap via vissa element gränser i trädet runtime är odefinierad.

trans-unit.source: Always use <xref:System.Windows.DependencyProperty.RegisterAttached%2A> to register properties where you specify <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata.Inherits%2A> in the metadata.
trans-unit.target: Använd alltid <xref:System.Windows.DependencyProperty.RegisterAttached%2A>att registrera egenskaper som anger du <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata.Inherits%2A>i metadata.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata.Inherits%2A> </xref:System.Windows.DependencyProperty.RegisterAttached%2A>
